#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.212"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.212:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.212:0.2"
msgid "21. Karajakāyavagga "
msgstr "21. The Body Born of Deeds "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.212:0.3"
msgid "212. Dutiyanirayasaggasutta "
msgstr "212. Heaven and Hell (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.212:1.1"
msgid "“Dasahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye. "
msgstr "“Someone with ten qualities is cast down to hell. "

msgctxt "an10.212:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi dasahi? "
msgstr "What ten? "

msgctxt "an10.212:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pāṇātipātī hoti luddo lohitapāṇi hatapahate niviṭṭho adayāpanno sabbapāṇabhūtesu. "
msgstr "It’s when a certain person kills living creatures. They’re violent, bloody-handed, a hardened killer, merciless to living beings. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.286, sc2
msgctxt "an10.212:2.1"
msgid "Adinnādāyī hoti … "
msgstr "They steal. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:2.2"
msgid "kāmesumicchācārī hoti … "
msgstr "They commit sexual misconduct. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:2.3"
msgid "musāvādī hoti … "
msgstr "They lie. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:2.4"
msgid "pisuṇavāco hoti … "
msgstr "They speak divisively. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:2.5"
msgid "pharusavāco hoti … "
msgstr "They speak harshly. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:2.6"
msgid "samphappalāpī hoti … "
msgstr "They indulge in talking nonsense. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:2.7"
msgid "abhijjhālu hoti … "
msgstr "They’re covetous. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:2.8"
msgid "byāpannacitto hoti … "
msgstr "They have cruel intentions. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:2.9"
msgid "micchādiṭṭhiko hoti viparītadassano: "
msgstr "They have wrong view. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:2.10"
msgid "‘natthi dinnaṃ … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an10.212:2.11"
msgid "sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedentī’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an10.212:2.12"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, dasahi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye. "
msgstr "Someone with these ten qualities is cast down to hell. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an10.212:3.1"
msgid "Dasahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge. "
msgstr "Someone with ten qualities is raised up to heaven. "

msgctxt "an10.212:3.2"
msgid "Katamehi dasahi? "
msgstr "What ten? "

msgctxt "an10.212:3.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pāṇātipātaṃ pahāya pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti nihitadaṇḍo nihitasattho lajjī dayāpanno, sabbapāṇabhūtahitānukampī viharati. "
msgstr "It’s when a certain person gives up killing living creatures. They renounce the rod and the sword. They’re scrupulous and kind, living full of compassion for all living beings. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an10.212:4.1"
msgid "Adinnādānaṃ pahāya adinnādānā paṭivirato hoti … "
msgstr "They give up stealing. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:4.2"
msgid "kāmesumicchācāraṃ pahāya kāmesumicchācārā paṭivirato hoti … "
msgstr "They give up sexual misconduct. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:4.3"
msgid "musāvādaṃ pahāya musāvādā paṭivirato hoti … "
msgstr "They give up lying. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:4.4"
msgid "pisuṇaṃ vācaṃ pahāya pisuṇāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti … "
msgstr "They give up divisive speech. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:4.5"
msgid "pharusaṃ vācaṃ pahāya pharusāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti … "
msgstr "They give up harsh speech. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:4.6"
msgid "samphappalāpaṃ pahāya samphappalāpā paṭivirato hoti … "
msgstr "They give up talking nonsense. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:4.7"
msgid "anabhijjhālu hoti … "
msgstr "They’re content. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:4.8"
msgid "abyāpannacitto hoti … "
msgstr "They’re kind hearted. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:4.9"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhiko hoti aviparītadassano: "
msgstr "They have right view. … "

msgctxt "an10.212:4.10"
msgid "‘atthi dinnaṃ … pe … ye imañca lokaṃ parañca lokaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedentī’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an10.212:4.11"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, dasahi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge”ti. "
msgstr "Someone with these ten qualities is raised up to heaven.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.212:4.12"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
